{"word":"ἔξεστι","slug":"ἔξεστι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἔξεστι</el></b> [impersonal verb 3 <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sg.\">sg.</a> of the unused <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔξειμι\">ἔξειμι</a></el>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐξουσία\">ἐξουσία</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ lit.\">lit.</a> ‘it is out/open’, hence <b>it is allowable/permitted/right <a href='B:470 12:2'>Mt 12:2</a>; <a href='B:470 14:4'>14:4</a>; <a href='B:470 22:17'>22:17</a>; <a href='B:500 5:10'>J 5:10</a>; <a href='B:510 8:37'>Ac 8:37</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:510 16:21'>16:21</a>; <a href='B:510 21:37'>21:37</a>; <a href='B:530 6:12'>1 Cor 6:12</a>.</b> The <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ptc.\">ptc.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐξόν\">ἐξόν</a></el> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> or without <el>ἐστίν</el> = <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔξεστι\">ἔξεστι</a></el> <b><a href='B:470 12:4'>Mt 12:4</a>; <a href='B:510 2:29'>Ac 2:29</a>; <a href='B:540 12:4'>2 Cor 12:4</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐξεστακέναι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐξέστραπται\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}